AddressInfo.Title: Best Western Premier Hotel International Brno
AddressInfo.AccessComments:
The hotel has the main entrance from Husova Street. However, the hotel's garage, where charging stations are located, can be reached from Besední Street, which lies below the hotel. The stations themselves are in the garages on the wall to the right of the exit.

TWO (2) stations 32A - 230V/400V right next to the exit, several (more than 15) Schuko outlets along the walls. Paid parking, CZK 60/hour. For Hotel guests 450,- CZK per 1 night stay. Charging is free.
